headline: Rentokil's Acquisition Of Terminix And Its Future, Why I'm Bullish
summary: Rentokil's acquisition of Terminix has been challenging, reducing ROIC from 10% to 6.1%. Read why I'm optimistic about RTO stock's upside potential.
